<li id="cite_note-Bush2004-6">
<span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Bush2004_6-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Bush2004_6-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222">
